latestIgtvVideos.title: best 10 yrs of my life
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
KVK proud to be a part this amazing institute which have given me a millions of memorable memories, knowledge, friends, best friend, best house/class. It feels like that day only i came to school for my admission and how come it became my last day.  Tears rolls down my cheeks the moment I remember my last day at school. It was a moment of painful parting. That day was my last chapter of the most glorious book of my life as a student. I spent 10 years as a student in my school. It was an unforgettable golden period for me. It passed away like a happiest dream. I and my fellow mates had a feeling of mixed joy & sorrow.
atlast thank you soo much @psk_universe for capturing all my beautiful moments....... i will miss KVK forever.... thank you KvK for making such a memorable 10 yrs of mine💞
and i will miss 10 b the most.....
#schoollife #will #miss #you #all #ist #igtv #farewell #kv #kvkhanapara
